uctcatalogservice on 10.233.33.139:53: server misbehaving' - 表明productcatalogservice存在DNS解析问题\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\", \n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice调用productcatalogservice的GetProduct操作，延迟从正常19.5ms增加到1413.6ms（72倍增长），表明下游服务不可达导致超时\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend服务出现大量HTTP 500错误（共263次），错误信息显示'failed to prepare order: failed to get product'，表明checkout服务异常导致前端服务失败\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现分析：\n\n**根因定位**：`productcatalogservice` 是问题的根本原因，因为：\n- 出现了265次DNS解析错误（状态码14）\n- 这是调用链中最下游的异常服务\n\n**影响传播路径**：\n1. `productcatalogservice` DNS解析失败（根因）\n2. `checkoutservice` 调用productcatalogservice超时（延迟增加72倍）\n3. `frontend` 调用checkoutservice失败，返回HTTP 500错误（受害者）\n\n**延迟分析**：\n- checkoutservice->productcatalogservice: 延迟从19.5ms增加到1413.6ms（72倍）\n- frontend->checkoutservice: 延迟从约150ms增加到约1.4s（9-10倍）\n\n**错误类型**：主要是DNS解析问题和连接超时，表明productcatalogservice的网络连接存在严重问题。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "consensus_decision": "AGREED", "current_hypothesis": "productcatalogservice is the root cause due to DNS resolution failures (connection error: desc = transport: Error while dialing dial tcp: lookup productcatalogservice on 10.233.33.139:53: server misbehaving)"}
